posts.post_title: Three T206 Six Card Lots - MOVED TO EBAY
posts.post_content:
I was just going to put these on eBay, but figured I'd give 'em a shot here first.  I've purchased a number of smaller lots in the last month or so and pulled out what I wanted to keep.  The Clancy and Parent were cracked out of PSA 1 holders.  The rest were purchased raw.

Three different six card lots; prices include delivery.  Take all 18 cards for $200.  Standard paypal preferred.
